00:14:53,840 --> 00:14:55,280
Captain is right about the rules.

273
00:14:56,040 --> 00:14:56,960
I'll accept the result.

274
00:14:57,760 --> 00:14:59,120
[Lu Xia] But I've decided

275
00:14:59,560 --> 00:15:01,680
to fight with everyone
to the end no matter what.

276
00:15:02,960 --> 00:15:04,760
This is what I long to do now.

277
00:15:08,240 --> 00:15:09,200
[Siyang] Okay.

278
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:12,360
You're part of Yu Qing, no matter what.

279
00:15:12,960 --> 00:15:14,320
Though you can't play in the match,

280
00:15:14,760 --> 00:15:17,320
there's something else for you to work on.

281
00:15:22,520 --> 00:15:24,320
All right, everyone else

282
00:15:24,760 --> 00:15:27,120
can go back to the court
and continue with the match.

283
00:15:30,320 --> 00:15:31,600
What are you waiting for?

284
00:15:34,480 --> 00:15:35,560
[scoffs]

285
00:15:57,080 --> 00:15:58,160
Do you have to do this?

286
00:15:58,880 --> 00:15:59,800
In fact...

287
00:16:00,480 --> 00:16:01,800
It's for his own good.

288
00:16:10,320 --> 00:16:11,840
[umpire 1] The match resumes now.

289
00:16:11,920 --> 00:16:13,040
TANG JIALE VS ZHANG BAIYANG

290
00:16:13,160 --> 00:16:14,800
ZHOU ZHI VS CHI DAYONG, SET 4-2

291
00:16:18,880 --> 00:16:19,920
[sighs]

292
00:16:20,600 --> 00:16:21,560
[moans]

293
00:16:31,000 --> 00:16:32,520
ZHOU ZHI VS CHI DAYONG, SET 4-2

294
00:16:35,920 --> 00:16:36,800
[grunts]

295
00:16:39,600 --> 00:16:42,200
Yan, has your data been fully updated?

296
00:16:42,920 --> 00:16:44,040
I'm looking forward to that.

297
00:16:44,600 --> 00:16:45,760
Let's try and see.

298
00:16:46,320 --> 00:16:47,160
By the way,

299
00:16:47,560 --> 00:16:49,440
remember to run 0.25 seconds
faster than usual

300
00:16:49,960 --> 00:16:51,880
when approaching the net,

301
00:16:51,960 --> 00:16:53,600
so that you can get
the best contact point.

302
00:16:55,000 --> 00:16:57,320
Don't worry. I won't show any mercy.

303
00:17:03,280 --> 00:17:05,280
[upbeat music]

304
00:17:12,119 --> 00:17:13,160
[camera shutter clicking]

305
00:17:15,560 --> 00:17:16,560
[grunts]

306
00:17:21,359 --> 00:17:23,240
Zhou Zhi won the set 6-3.

307
00:17:23,319 --> 00:17:25,040
Zhou Zhi is doing well today.

308
00:17:30,319 --> 00:17:31,800
Is Dachi not feeling well?

309
00:17:32,359 --> 00:17:33,280
[grunts]

310
00:17:33,840 --> 00:17:35,840
Qiao Chen doesn't seem
to be performing at his level.

311
00:17:36,880 --> 00:17:38,600
It seems that
Yan put him at a disadvantage.

312
00:17:39,280 --> 00:17:41,000
It's not Qiao Chen
who isn't performing well.

313
00:17:41,080 --> 00:17:43,520
It's because Yan has improved.

314
00:17:46,200 --> 00:17:48,040
[Siyang] Over these two months
before the match,

315
00:17:48,120 --> 00:17:52,240
Yan not only collected data
from our opponents to help us,

316
00:17:52,320 --> 00:17:54,520
but he, in fact, collected our data, too.

317
00:17:55,200 --> 00:17:57,400
Yan keeps improving.

318
00:18:01,520 --> 00:18:03,320
The match is over.
Yan Zhiming is the winner.

319
00:18:18,040 --> 00:18:19,120
[sighs]

320
00:18:21,840 --> 00:18:23,040
It's not a bad thing

321
00:18:23,840 --> 00:18:25,400
to lose a match now.

322
00:18:32,080 --> 00:18:34,520
[panting]

323
00:18:46,000 --> 00:18:46,920
[Coach Qi] Siyang.

324
00:18:47,840 --> 00:18:49,880
This is the list of players
against Xing Yao.

325
00:18:50,720 --> 00:18:52,040
Qiao Chen and Huang Jing

326
00:18:52,520 --> 00:18:54,840
are on the bench list
to be number one and two.

327
00:18:55,960 --> 00:18:57,840
You haven't fully recovered
from your injuries,

328
00:18:59,040 --> 00:19:00,760
so I arranged an extra main player

329
00:19:00,840 --> 00:19:02,960
according to the results
of the qualifying competition.

330
00:19:03,040 --> 00:19:05,000
[sighs sharply]
Coach, I got it.

331
00:19:05,080 --> 00:19:07,360
I'll announce the list later.

332
00:19:08,440 --> 00:19:09,520
Okay.

333
00:19:14,560 --> 00:19:17,360
LIST OF MAIN PLAYERS
OF THE YU QING TENNIS CLUB

334
00:19:18,880 --> 00:19:20,880
[light music]

335
00:19:34,640 --> 00:19:36,640
[light music continues]

336
00:19:48,800 --> 00:19:50,400
[Lian] Isn't this place quite familiar?

337
00:19:53,920 --> 00:19:54,920
[gasps]

338
00:19:57,400 --> 00:19:58,400
Liu Lian?

339
00:19:59,840 --> 00:20:01,080
I'm not late, aren't I?

340
00:20:01,560 --> 00:20:04,000
LIU LIAN
HAI GUANG HIGH SCHOOL PLAYER

341
00:20:04,600 --> 00:20:05,720
[sighs]

342
00:20:05,800 --> 00:20:07,320
Hmm. Exactly on time.

343
00:20:11,880 --> 00:20:13,400
You already knew it was me, didn't you?

344
00:20:13,480 --> 00:20:15,000
When I saw your ID,

345
00:20:15,080 --> 00:20:16,600
"Pavlov's Dog,"

346
00:20:17,200 --> 00:20:18,600
I was pretty sure that it was you.

347
00:20:21,480 --> 00:20:22,320
I didn't expect

348
00:20:22,600 --> 00:20:24,360
that the one interacting with me
would be you.

349
00:20:24,760 --> 00:20:27,920
I tried to drop hints in different ways.

350
00:20:29,080 --> 00:20:30,160
For example,

351
00:20:31,200 --> 00:20:32,880
why I chose this café.

352
00:20:37,840 --> 00:20:39,480
This was the park

353
00:20:40,480 --> 00:20:42,160
where we played a match for the last time.

354
00:20:43,240 --> 00:20:44,960
If I hadn't moved,

355
00:20:46,640 --> 00:20:47,800
the competition between us

356
00:20:48,320 --> 00:20:50,040
would have continued until now.

357
00:20:51,960 --> 00:20:53,960
[light music]

358
00:20:58,520 --> 00:21:00,400
[both panting]

359
00:21:02,840 --> 00:21:03,880
[grunting]

360
00:21:10,520 --> 00:21:11,440
V, GO DOWN FIGHTING

361
00:21:12,400 --> 00:21:13,640
Do you remember these?

362
00:21:17,840 --> 00:21:18,920
How could I not remember?

363
00:21:24,080 --> 00:21:24,920
And this.

364
00:21:25,480 --> 00:21:28,160
[Lian] In fact, I quite miss
the tennis court.

365
00:21:28,640 --> 00:21:31,480
For this ball,
the odds of going right are 73.2%.

366
00:21:32,000 --> 00:21:33,640
The angle is about 65 degrees.

367
00:21:33,720 --> 00:21:35,360
-[thwacks]
-Wrong.

368
00:21:35,440 --> 00:21:37,200
The odds should be 81.9%.

369
00:21:38,640 --> 00:21:40,240
And I'll get one point with a drop shot.

370
00:21:42,680 --> 00:21:44,680
5-4. I got one more point than you.

371
00:21:44,760 --> 00:21:46,240
No, your calculation is wrong.

372
00:21:46,840 --> 00:21:48,600
[chuckles]
Let's go.

373
00:21:51,320 --> 00:21:52,480
[young Yan Zhiming sighs]

374
00:21:55,120 --> 00:21:56,320
You can't calculate like this.

375
00:21:56,400 --> 00:21:57,840
That should be normal distribution.

376
00:21:58,680 --> 00:22:01,640
You see, that's 81.9.

377
00:22:02,200 --> 00:22:03,080
It can't be.

378
00:22:03,960 --> 00:22:06,000
-[chuckles]
-That should be binomial distribution.

379
00:22:06,080 --> 00:22:07,960
You see, that's 73.2.

380
00:22:10,760 --> 00:22:12,760
[light music]

381
00:22:24,720 --> 00:22:27,800
Zhiming, why don't we stop here today?

382
00:22:28,160 --> 00:22:29,080
Why?

383
00:22:29,480 --> 00:22:30,600
The match isn't over.

384
00:22:30,680 --> 00:22:32,120
Go home and do the math.

385
00:22:32,200 --> 00:22:33,760
Let's continue the match next time.

386
00:22:33,840 --> 00:22:35,360
We'll see who's the winner.

387
00:22:38,320 --> 00:22:40,880
-The next time will be the decisive match.
-Right.

388
00:22:41,600 --> 00:22:42,680
Right.

389
00:22:43,760 --> 00:22:44,680
[sighs]

390
00:22:59,520 --> 00:23:02,120
I can't believe we still have a chance

391
00:23:02,200 --> 00:23:03,920
to come back to this tennis court.

392
00:23:04,920 --> 00:23:06,160
Do you still remember

393
00:23:07,560 --> 00:23:08,480
the unfinished match?

394
00:23:08,880 --> 00:23:10,800
Seven years, two months, and fifteen days.

395
00:23:12,200 --> 00:23:13,160
I can still remember it.

396
00:23:18,760 --> 00:23:19,600
[sighs]

397
00:23:20,160 --> 00:23:21,520
Hai Guang High School.

398
00:23:23,040 --> 00:23:26,640
If we hadn't met today
and we both beat our opponents,

399
00:23:27,920 --> 00:23:30,440
we would have met
in the provincial finals.

400
00:23:31,880 --> 00:23:33,600
Let's keep our promise

401
00:23:34,520 --> 00:23:36,120
to fulfill the unfinished match.

402
00:23:38,480 --> 00:23:39,600
Is this what you're thinking?

403
00:23:41,280 --> 00:23:43,280
[light music]

404
00:23:51,720 --> 00:23:52,800
Of course.

405
00:24:04,840 --> 00:24:06,520
[Young Lian] Don't forget
to keep your word.

406
00:24:20,560 --> 00:24:21,680
[chuckles]

407
00:24:27,720 --> 00:24:29,720
[playful music]

408
00:24:29,800 --> 00:24:30,640
Qiao Chen!

409
00:24:31,960 --> 00:24:32,840
[Qiao Chen] Xing Zi!

410
00:24:33,360 --> 00:24:34,320
What are you doing here?

411
00:24:35,480 --> 00:24:36,360
What a coincidence.

412
00:24:36,960 --> 00:24:38,240
And why are you here?

413
00:24:40,760 --> 00:24:42,000
I'm thinking here.

414
00:24:46,840 --> 00:24:48,040
"Thinking"?

415
00:24:49,600 --> 00:24:51,240
People use brains to think.

416
00:24:51,560 --> 00:24:53,120
I use my stomach.

417
00:24:53,200 --> 00:24:54,120
[chuckles]

418
00:24:56,600 --> 00:24:58,200
The national tournament is coming up.

419
00:24:58,280 --> 00:25:00,480
Why aren't you training?
Why are you staring blankly here?

420
00:25:02,080 --> 00:25:03,200
[exhales sharply]

421
00:25:03,280 --> 00:25:05,960
I lost
at the qualifying competition yesterday.

422
00:25:06,880 --> 00:25:09,440
I can't play the match against Xing Yao.

423
00:25:12,040 --> 00:25:14,320
Isn't your goal the national tournament?

424
00:25:14,400 --> 00:25:16,440
You can't play this time,
but there's still next time.

425
00:25:17,000 --> 00:25:19,040
I tried really hard this time.

426
00:25:19,120 --> 00:25:21,680
But I didn't expect the others
to make so much progress.

427
00:25:23,560 --> 00:25:26,280
Is it only because
the others made much progress?

428
00:25:27,680 --> 00:25:28,600
Mm-hm.

429
00:25:29,160 --> 00:25:30,200
No other reasons?

430
00:25:33,160 --> 00:25:34,120
[sighs]

431
00:25:36,480 --> 00:25:37,320
All right.

432
00:25:39,920 --> 00:25:41,240
How about playing a match with me?

433
00:25:43,040 --> 00:25:44,000
With you?

434
00:25:44,080 --> 00:25:44,920
Mm-hm.

435
00:25:47,520 --> 00:25:49,520
[upbeat music]

436
00:26:03,360 --> 00:26:05,360
[upbeat music continues]

437
00:26:08,400 --> 00:26:11,880
Is it kind of bullying?

438
00:26:16,640 --> 00:26:18,360
Watch out. I'm going to serve.

439
00:26:19,560 --> 00:26:20,480
[snickers]

440
00:26:23,120 --> 00:26:23,960
[grunts]

441
00:26:29,200 --> 00:26:30,240
[groans]

442
00:26:31,880 --> 00:26:33,840
[Qiao Chen] It's surprising
that the slim Xing Zi

443
00:26:33,920 --> 00:26:35,360
can hit such a powerful serve.

444
00:26:38,040 --> 00:26:38,960
It seems that

445
00:26:39,640 --> 00:26:42,800
I can't judge an opponent's shots
by their appearance.

446
00:26:43,080 --> 00:26:45,920
If I make a wrong judgement,
I'll feel nervous.

447
00:26:46,600 --> 00:26:48,040
In any situation,

448
00:26:48,240 --> 00:26:50,440
being unobservant at any moment is fatal.

449
00:26:54,920 --> 00:26:57,840
I should always treat my opponent
like a heavy rock.

450
00:26:58,960 --> 00:27:01,560
I should always be keen
to face challenges.

451
00:27:05,200 --> 00:27:06,200
[grunts]

452
00:27:09,640 --> 00:27:10,640
[chuckles]

453
00:27:12,200 --> 00:27:13,040
Fantastic!

454
00:27:17,640 --> 00:27:19,360
You've become the original Qiao Chen.

455
00:27:19,440 --> 00:27:20,920
Thank you, Xing Zi.

456
00:27:25,160 --> 00:27:27,160
[romantic music]

457
00:27:43,320 --> 00:27:45,000
[Coach Qi] Do you know
that what you've done

458
00:27:45,080 --> 00:27:46,520
is an irresponsible act for yourself?

459
00:27:47,040 --> 00:27:48,000
[Siyang] I know.

460
00:27:48,480 --> 00:27:50,440
The injury on your left arm
isn't fully recovered.

461
00:27:50,520 --> 00:27:52,560
You disobeyed the medical order
and started training.

462
00:27:52,640 --> 00:27:55,600
Do you want to permanently injure
your left arm and stop playing tennis?

463
00:27:59,240 --> 00:28:03,360
4 DAYS BEFORE YU QING VS XING YAO

464
00:28:13,160 --> 00:28:15,160
[calm music]

465
00:28:22,680 --> 00:28:23,760
[sighs]

466
00:28:28,960 --> 00:28:30,000
[chuckles]

467
00:28:39,920 --> 00:28:40,760
Class.

468
00:28:41,320 --> 00:28:43,640
I've marked all the papers
of the language test.

469
00:28:43,720 --> 00:28:45,440
The one improving the most in our class

470
00:28:46,000 --> 00:28:47,160
is Lu Xia.

471
00:28:48,240 --> 00:28:51,040
Did you all know that
he can make sentences with idioms?

472
00:28:51,520 --> 00:28:52,640
[all chuckle]

473
00:28:53,200 --> 00:28:54,520
To encourage him,

474
00:28:54,760 --> 00:28:57,000
as a teacher,
I decided to give you a present.

475
00:28:57,480 --> 00:28:58,640
Come here, Lu Xia.

476
00:28:59,640 --> 00:29:01,840
-[student 1] Present.
-[student 2] Good to have a present.

477
00:29:02,320 --> 00:29:03,440
[student 3] I'm so envious.

478
00:29:05,160 --> 00:29:06,480
-Thank you.
-Keep up the good work.

479
00:29:06,560 --> 00:29:07,400
Mm-hm.

480
00:29:09,200 --> 00:29:11,280
If I had come back from abroad, too...

481
00:29:15,480 --> 00:29:16,400
Lu Xia.

482
00:29:16,720 --> 00:29:18,280
[school bell tolling]

483
00:29:18,920 --> 00:29:20,320
[teacher] Okay, class dismissed.

484
00:29:21,920 --> 00:29:22,840
[student clears throat]

485
00:29:22,920 --> 00:29:23,960
-[student 4] Let's get lunch.
-[student 5] I'm hungry.

486
00:29:24,040 --> 00:29:25,800
-[student 6] Okay, see you later.
-[student 5] I'm so hungry.

487
00:29:25,880 --> 00:29:27,400
-[student 7] Let's buy some food.
-[student 8] Drink some water

488
00:29:27,480 --> 00:29:28,320
and take a rest.

489
00:29:37,280 --> 00:29:38,320
You can have it.

490
00:29:39,000 --> 00:29:41,000
[light music]

491
00:29:41,480 --> 00:29:44,040
Lu Xia, is this a big improvement?

492
00:29:44,520 --> 00:29:47,720
[Mu] Every day, I start my warm-up
by doing some juggling.

493
00:29:47,800 --> 00:29:49,440
-It's full of ups and downs.
-[giggles]

494
00:29:49,520 --> 00:29:51,080
What were you writing?

495
00:29:51,320 --> 00:29:53,960
I could write better with my feet.
[chuckles]

496
00:29:54,480 --> 00:29:58,000
[Ying] Is this a present for me?

497
00:29:59,640 --> 00:30:00,880
[chuckles]

498
00:30:08,800 --> 00:30:10,920
[indistinct chatter]

499
00:30:13,680 --> 00:30:15,480
HUA CHONGHONG

500
00:30:15,640 --> 00:30:16,880
YOU SHIXING

501
00:30:16,960 --> 00:30:19,680
[Tang Jiale] Why does no one invite us
to a photoshoot for a magazine?

502
00:30:19,760 --> 00:30:21,120
This person doesn't look like this.

503
00:30:21,200 --> 00:30:23,320
-[Qiao Chen] That's right.
-The photo looks much better.

504
00:30:23,400 --> 00:30:24,720
It's just like faking photos.

505
00:30:24,800 --> 00:30:26,400
[Coach Qi] This isn't a fashion magazine.

506
00:30:26,480 --> 00:30:28,240
-[Tang Jiale gasps]
-[all] Coach.

507
00:30:28,320 --> 00:30:29,240
[Coach Qi] Have a seat.

508
00:30:33,520 --> 00:30:34,520
[gasps]

509
00:30:35,200 --> 00:30:37,680
Yue Yang and You Shixing

510
00:30:38,520 --> 00:30:40,560
are always the first doubles players
of Xing Yao.

511
00:30:40,640 --> 00:30:42,280
It's their version of golden partners.

512
00:30:42,720 --> 00:30:44,680
-Mm-hm.
-You've already played against them,

513
00:30:44,760 --> 00:30:46,240
so I won't talk about them much today.

514
00:30:46,320 --> 00:30:49,200
Coach, only Dachi has played
a match against them

515
00:30:49,280 --> 00:30:50,520
because we were split.

516
00:30:50,600 --> 00:30:52,880
So, this year, is it....

517
00:30:55,680 --> 00:30:57,000
CHI DAYONG, DOUBLES NUMBER ONE

518
00:30:57,440 --> 00:31:01,040
Yes! Dachi, that's great.
[laughs]

519
00:31:02,360 --> 00:31:04,720
What are you doing?
I'm not done. Why are you so excited?

520
00:31:05,160 --> 00:31:07,080
Huh? Coach, it's because

521
00:31:07,160 --> 00:31:09,880
the surname starting with "T" on our team

522
00:31:09,960 --> 00:31:10,880
is mine, right?

523
00:31:11,840 --> 00:31:12,840
So clever.

524
00:31:13,320 --> 00:31:16,040
CHI DAYONG AND

525
00:31:18,320 --> 00:31:20,680
[gasps, sighs sharply]

526
00:31:22,520 --> 00:31:28,440
CHI DAYONG AND TANG JIALE,
DOUBLES NUMBER ONE

527
00:31:30,480 --> 00:31:33,040
Coach, you really scared me.

528
00:31:33,120 --> 00:31:34,720
Dachi, that's amazing.

529
00:31:34,800 --> 00:31:36,440
We can finally play tennis together.

530
00:31:36,520 --> 00:31:37,840
-[Tang Jiale laughs]
-[Dayong] Yes.

531
00:31:38,440 --> 00:31:40,960
MU SIYANG, SINGLES NUMBER ONE
ZHOU ZHI, SINGLES NUMBER TWO

532
00:31:41,040 --> 00:31:44,720
Why did you leave the third singles blank?

533
00:31:45,280 --> 00:31:49,080
You, Baiyang, and Yan Zhiming.

534
00:31:50,080 --> 00:31:53,560
In fact, you three are better
at playing singles.

535
00:31:54,120 --> 00:31:56,360
I'm going to pick two out of you three

536
00:31:56,680 --> 00:31:58,360
to form the best doubles for us.

537
00:31:59,000 --> 00:32:00,480
But I haven't thought it through.

538
00:32:03,480 --> 00:32:05,600
Coach, Baiyang and I

539
00:32:06,200 --> 00:32:07,720
