551
00:32:38,200 --> 00:32:40,600
In the second quarter,

552
00:32:40,920 --> 00:32:43,280
-we--
-Are you saying you will deliberately lose

553
00:32:43,360 --> 00:32:44,720
in their service game?

554
00:32:44,800 --> 00:32:47,160
