00:33:44,920 --> 00:33:46,880
-The failure rate can be--
-So, you can try to use

571
00:33:46,960 --> 00:33:48,040
your high-speed serve.

572
00:33:50,720 --> 00:33:51,640
[Baiyang] By the way,

573
00:33:52,960 --> 00:33:54,360
