574
00:33:57,160 --> 00:33:58,240
[sighs]

575
00:34:07,240 --> 00:34:08,280
[clears throat]

576
00:34:11,159 --> 00:34:14,120
Mm! Since it has been decided

577
00:34:14,520 --> 00:34:15,840
that we'll play the doubles match,

578
00:34:16,760 --> 00:34:20,239
you can, of course, propose your plan,
just like how we usually do.

579
00:34:21,120 --> 00:34:23,840
