616
00:36:52,040 --> 00:36:53,920
I'm not joking.

617
00:36:54,280 --> 00:36:57,120
Don't you think Chi Dayong
looks like he's under a lot of pressure?

618
00:36:57,680 --> 00:36:58,800
Hey. Tell me.

