00:37:27,880 --> 00:37:29,840
[gasps]
This is impossible.

629
00:37:30,320 --> 00:37:34,120
Look. He's always been good at studying.
He's been helping me review lessons.

630
00:37:35,000 --> 00:37:37,560
Or perhaps it's because
of the pressure of the tournament.

631
00:37:39,200 --> 00:37:40,560
That's also impossible.

632
00:37:41,000 --> 00:37:42,040
Why is it impossible?

633
00:37:42,520 --> 00:37:44,480
Didn't you notice
that I worked very hard recently?

634
00:37:44,560 --> 00:37:45,760
I've never slacked off.

635
00:37:45,840 --> 00:37:46,840
[snickers]

636
00:37:47,360 --> 00:37:48,400
You did work hard.

637
00:37:48,800 --> 00:37:51,760
But Dachi looks quite normal to me.
Nothing's strange about him.

638
00:37:53,960 --> 00:37:56,240
